

actor "CI/CD System" as CICD
actor WebPlatform

participant QueueService
participant "Google Cloud Tasks" as GCT
participant "Pipecat Tester Service" as Pipecat

CICD -> WebPlatform : /1/ POST /api/v1/simulations
CICD -> WebPlatform : /2/ GET /api/v1/simulations/{simulationId} (short polling)


WebPlatform -> QueueService : /3/ POST /create-task
QueueService -> GCT : /4/ create task
activate GCT
GCT -> WebPlatform : /5/ POST /api/call/process-call
deactivate GCT
WebPlatform -> Pipecat : /6/ POST /initiate_phone_call
WebPlatform -> Pipecat : /7/ GET /call_status/{callSid} (short polling)

